### ðŸ”§ Code with Comments:

```scl
// Set assumed PLC scan cycle time (in seconds)
// Adjust this if your OB cycle time is different
#CycleTime := 0.005; // 5 ms

// Calculate ramp step size based on rate (units/sec) and cycle time
#Step := #Ramp_Rate * #CycleTime;

// Select target value based on ramp direction
IF #Enable_Up THEN
    #Target := #Target_Up;
ELSIF #Enable_Down THEN
    #Target := #Target_Down;
ELSE
    #Target := #Out; // Hold current value if neither enabled
END_IF;

// Ramp logic â€“ adjust output value toward target
IF (#Target > #Out) AND #Enable_Up THEN
    // Ramp upward, but clamp at target
    #Out := MIN_REAL(IN1 := #Out + #Step, IN2 := #Target);
ELSIF (#Target < #Out) AND #Enable_Down THEN
    // Ramp downward, but clamp at target
    #Out := MAX_REAL(IN1 := #Target, IN2 := #Out - #Step);
END_IF;
```

---

### ðŸ“‹ Variable Table Documentation:

| Name          | Type | Default | Description                                                |
| ------------- | ---- | ------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| `Target_Up`   | REAL | 0.0     | Target value to ramp up toward when `Enable_Up = TRUE`     |
| `Target_Down` | REAL | 0.0     | Target value to ramp down toward when `Enable_Down = TRUE` |
| `Enable_Up`   | BOOL | FALSE   | When TRUE, ramps output up toward `Target_Up`              |
| `Enable_Down` | BOOL | FALSE   | When TRUE, ramps output down toward `Target_Down`          |
| `Ramp_Rate`   | REAL | 0.0     | Ramp speed in units per second                             |
| `Out`         | REAL | 0.0     | Current ramped output value                                |

**Static Variables (internal memory, retained across scans):**

| Name        | Type | Default | Description                                               |
| ----------- | ---- | ------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| `Target`    | REAL | 0.0     | Currently selected target (up or down)                    |
| `NowTime`   | TIME | T#0ms   | \[Reserved] For future time-based ramping                 |
| `DeltaTime` | REAL | 0.0     | \[Reserved] For future use if calculating real delta time |
| `Step`      | REAL | 0.0     | Current step size calculated from rate and cycle time     |
| `CycleTime` | REAL | 0.0     | PLC cycle time in seconds (set to 0.005 for 5ms)          |

